Usage: reportVoltage [-help] [-quiet] [-view <string>]
                     [-term <string> | -net <string> | -inst <string>]
                     [-early | -late]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-early                     # early mode (default late) (bool, optional)
-inst <string>             # inst name or pointer (string, optional)
-late                      # late mode (bool, optional)
-net <string>              # net name or pointer (string, optional)
-quiet                     # only return the voltage and not printing
                           # information (bool, optional)
-term <string>             # term name or pointer (string, optional)
-view <string>             # analysis view (string, optional)